Mogens C. Bay 
Executive Compensation
As Chairman and Chief Executive Officer at VALMONT INDUSTRIES INC, Mogens C. Bay  made $5,441,288 in total compensation.  Of this total $980,000 was received as a salary, $722,260 was received as a bonus, $1,700,589 was received in stock options, $1,715,000 was awarded as stock and $323,439 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


