Insider Activity


Individual




Mogens C. Bay



Mr. Mogens C. Bay is Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at Valmont Industries, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Father Flanagan's Boys' Home. 
Mr. Bay was previously employed as Independent Director by ConAgra Foods, Inc. and Vice Chairman by The Nebraska Medical Center. He also served on the board at Level 3 Communications, Inc. and Peter Kiewit Son's, Inc.



